import React from 'react' import './Profile.css' import {useSelector} from "react-redux"; import ifollowers from '../../assets/icon-visability-shared.png' import ifollowing from '../../assets/icon-visability-provate.png' export const Profile = () => { const state = useSelector(state => state.user) const {avatar_url, login, name, followers, following, html_url} = state.user return (
{name}
{login}
{followers} followers
{following}
following
) }
